{"tid":481313,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂］分享戲院睇戲不快經歷","createTime":"2017-11-27T05:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T13:57:42.000Z","uid":39576,"like":86,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5c17cf989e8684bb18146a5428a303df4cf1ea","tid":481313,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"戲院硬件問題：例如地點隔攝、要行十幾層先上到個院、坐位零斜度俾前面遮到、環境污糟、冷氣太凍、員工無禮貌⋯<br />\n<br />\n以上我都忍到覺得小事，最大問題係觀眾<br />\n<br />\n- 遲到慢慢行入場<br />\n- 食野勁大味或者發出勁多膠袋聲<br />\n- 帶小朋友睇大人戲<br />\n- 唔熄電話任佢響<br />\n- 開電話掃mon覆whatsapp<br />\n- 人肉旁白講畫面有乜、懶醒估劇情<br />\n- 見血腥暴力場面會：「啐啐啐」、「痴線㗎」<br />\n- 鳩笑<br />\n- 鼻鼾聲<br />\n- 唔知係咪凍得濟既搓手聲（連續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n如果發生喺我隔離左右我都第一時間屌，但無奈香港人面皮無限厚，尋晚個廢老夫婦就係叫極都要傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後想講各位分享發洩完，如果身邊有朋友係咁要即刻指正，屋企有老人家會去睇戲既多d陪佢地去控制下，睇戲時有咩仆街唔好怕麻煩或者驚影響到人而唔屌，係唔好諗要即屌！"},{"pid":"fb1b6578b2e836c1a20922b973ec2d29c1045cc6","tid":481313,"uid":49978,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"踢登<br />\n頂登<br />\n腳dum地打拍子<br />\n開mon熄mon<br />\n屌極都有真係"},{"pid":"7693ea172d6cc36f4698c891beb877760a1ea621","tid":481313,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"討論劇情又唔知人地聽到 全場得佢2個把聲"},{"pid":"b60a36d65480c5be9673b1e0d2b470a4fb877048","tid":481313,"uid":6436,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUS5bS8Y7QPA&d=0cG%2BRrl715dhc6BfT2jbW54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=78bd43d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA</a>"},{"pid":"170448b9560ee93cefe63a12d11f86762da7c00b","tid":481313,"uid":76068,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"帶住個過度活躍嘅小朋友睇戲，又唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8112d444e9c0cc0d01d3b14edb14d5627c4dbb3","tid":481313,"uid":39576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:29:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>討論劇情又唔知人地聽到 全場得佢2個把聲</blockquote><br />\nD人好中意懶係壓低聲線傾計，唔知人地都係會聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f641cc1c3206b5a1d0ced42875e568b69dc5e5b8","tid":481313,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶住個過度活躍嘅小朋友睇戲，又唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前睇玻璃城堡有一家人個女仔（應該中學）狂覆述畫面有咩，叫極都唔停，坐佢隔離個老母又好野成尊佛咁唔郁唔理定晒咁睇戲，同套戲既劇情好大諷刺"},{"pid":"cf8215433b0c5cd60504a286241ee564af0596ac","tid":481313,"uid":159196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"試過睇戲個陣成套戲都勁嘈勁大聲，但後面有人鼻鼾聲大到咁嘈ge環境我同個朋友都聽得勁清楚佢ge鼻鼾聲"},{"pid":"684b44b7f99144c5cf9714c257e795b59812a6e4","tid":481313,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUS5bS8Y7QPA&d=0cG%2BRrl715dhc6BfT2jbW54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=78bd43d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA</a></blockquote><br />\n我都有睇howtin，所以先出呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad2c93a9305b43a16002216ca77ff0140febab","tid":481313,"uid":6436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUS5bS8Y7QPA&d=0cG%2BRrl715dhc6BfT2jbW54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=78bd43d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/US5bS8Y7QPA</a></blockquote><br />\n我都有睇howtin，所以先出呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢鬧